INTRODUCTION
Play Tic Tac Toe Game on your Google Chrome Browser with our simple & lightweight extension - No Internet required, no annoying ADS, and 100% Free!

HOW TO INSTALL?
1. Click "Add to Chrome" to install the extension
2. Pin the Tic Tac Toe Game extension icon to the Chrome toolbar
3. Click the  Tic Tac Toe Game icon on the Chrome toolbar, the Tic Tac Toe Game popup will open. Tap on the popup or press "Spacebar" to start ;)
That's all you need to do! Have fun!
You also can play more games on the popup
